latestPosts.caption:
KASHI to KAILASH releases globally via Godmother Records on FEB 21 2025 🔱🏔️

2 years ago I was called to make this project when my tour was cancelled. Nothing made sense and it felt like my dreams were impossible. I asked Shiva what my next step was…he told me to SURRENDER 🙏🏽

This album is my humble offering on the altar of Saraswati. @larrazanacho and I made this entire project, from beginning to release in 28 days. This is my 5th studio album, but it feels like it’s my rebirth🧿

Remember…if GOD is for you…who can be against you? 

Har Har Mahadev 🔱

👑 The queen is back for year 4 of Masala Mixtape. @therajakumari

Grammy-nominated rapper, singer, songwriter, and classically trained Indian-American, Raja Kumari, is taking over Brooklyn on July 26th.

She bridges the worlds of traditional Indian music and global hip-hop culture.

She’s been busy: 
✨ Writing hits for Gwen Stefani, Fall Out Boy & Iggy Azalea 
✨ Winning a BMI Pop Award and snagging that Grammy nom 
✨ Dropping tracks on Coachella’s stage 
✨ Picking up a VMA for “Renegade” with Stefflon Don 
✨ Oh, and founding her own label, Godmother Records

Catch her energy and sound live on our stage this year on July 26th.

Masala Mixtape / 15+ Artists
South Asian Music Festival / Year 4

🎟️Ticket link in bio.
